{:* ─── Hero Section ─── *:}
<div class="border rounded-4 p-4 p-md-5 mb-5 text-center bg-body-tertiary">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-12 col-lg-9 col-xl-8">
            <span class="badge border text-body-secondary text-uppercase px-3 py-2 mb-3"
                  >
                Kit de Démarrage Open-Source
            </span>
            <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold mb-3">Neutral TS Starter Py</h1>
            <p class="lead text-body-secondary mb-4 mx-auto">
                Un kit de démarrage modulaire et opinionné pour construire des
                <strong class="text-body">Applications Web Progressives</strong> en utilisant
                <strong class="text-body">Python&nbsp;(Flask)</strong> pour le backend et
                <strong class="text-body">Neutral&nbsp;TS</strong> comme moteur de templates universel.
            </p>
            <div class="d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-center gap-2 mb-4">
                <span class="badge border rounded-pill text-body-secondary px-3 py-2">🐍 Flask</span>
                <span class="badge border rounded-pill text-body-secondary px-3 py-2">📱 PWA Ready</span>
                <span class="badge border rounded-pill text-body-secondary px-3 py-2">🧩 Neutral TS</span>
                <span class="badge border rounded-pill text-body-secondary px-3 py-2">🔒 Sécurité</span>
                <span class="badge border rounded-pill text-body-secondary px-3 py-2">🌐 i18n</span>
            </div>
            <div class="d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-center gap-3">
                <a href="https://github.com/FranBarInstance/neutral-starter-py"
                   target="_blank"
                   class="btn btn-dark btn-lg px-4">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18"
                         fill="currentColor" class="me-2 mb-1" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
